Amar clinical psychologist amake bolche je amar kauke dekha dorkar. Ami bhebhechilam amar kauke dekhar dorkar nei karon amar sathe kichu bhul chhilo na. Amar sobematro hridrogo chhilo. Ebong jokhon tini paramorsh dichhilen je ami kauke dekhte pai, tokhon etir kono mane chhilo na. Kintu jehetu ami khub bishonno chhilam, eto dure chole giyechilam, ami, amar swami amar swamir madhyame, ami bhebhechilam ami chesta kori ebong shudhu ekta suyog ghrano kori ebong shudhu karo kotha shuni ba kauke amar kotha shunte dey, karon ami nishchit chhilam na je eti kii jorito. Ami age kono clinical psychologist-er kache jaini. Tai ekti clinical psychologist hishabe amar kache ekti sankochon chhilo, apnar mostishker moddhe oboshshoi guruttor kichhu bhul chhilo ja apnake ekti clinical psychologist-er sathe dekha korte hobe ebong amar kauke dekhar dorkar nei. Kintu Mita o jokhon korechhilo tokhon bujhlam heart surgeryr jonno opokkho korte mone porena. Ami talikay amar nam rakhechi. Ebong mojar bapar holo, ekjon mohila hishabe, apni onubhob koren je apni onno karo kandhe kandte pare. Kintu prothombar, shudhu amar abeg tar kache prokash korechi. Ebong jinisgulike ber kore daoar maddhome, eti amake bujhte sahayyo korechhilo je ami ki anubhav korchhilam karon beshi samoy amra jinisgulike botal kore rakhi, amra kabhu segulike ber korte dibo na ba amra kabhu amader moddhe naki ami jinishgulike bojhate chai na ebong ebong tokhon amader chokhe jol ashche ebong amar hridoy fulche karon ami jani na je onno keu eti korte pare na.
